data.description: Welcome home to this cozy 3-bedroom and 2-bathroom with 1,350 Sq feet in South Tampa.  Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the seamless flow of the main living area. The home has Carpet in the bedrooms and wood and tile in the living room, dining room, and kitchen area. The kitchen is equipped with a refrigerator, stove dishwasher, and microwave and tile Countertops. The washer and dryer are a plus. No HOA or CDD fees. The property is conveniently located just minutes to the Gandy Bridge and Crosstown Expressway and only 10 minutes from I-275; 15 minutes to Tampa International Airport, Hyde Park Village, International Plaza, and the Veteran’s Expressway, and less than 10 minutes to Bayshore Boulevard.
